06:38.432 --> 06:41.466
[ dogs snorting ]

06:44.837 --> 06:47.539
[ barking ]

06:47.541 --> 06:51.209
Flynn: Looks like
a girl's scrunchie.

06:51.211 --> 06:53.945
I'll get the command center
up here.

06:53.947 --> 06:55.781
Call the captain.

06:55.783 --> 06:58.116
[ police radio chatter ]

06:58.118 --> 07:00.719
Well, I don't know
if it's good news or bad,

07:00.721 --> 07:02.053
But I'm pretty sure
it belongs to michelle.

07:02.055 --> 07:03.622
Oh, god.

07:03.624 --> 07:06.625
Well, I may have the guy
who can tell us how it fell off.

07:06.627 --> 07:08.627
[ camera shutter clicking ]

07:08.629 --> 07:10.595
How'd you scratch yourself,
lewis?

07:10.597 --> 07:14.800
It must have happened
when you beat me.

07:14.802 --> 07:16.635
Any luck?
Buzz:
Well, if you call

07:16.637 --> 07:19.638
