facial-recognition program.

07:21.475 --> 07:22.607
Good. I'll need it.

07:22.609 --> 07:23.942
Rusty: Hey, buzz.

07:23.944 --> 07:25.277
Lieutenant, you remember kris,
don't you?

07:26.112 --> 07:27.579
