07:37.057 --> 07:39.124
What are you looking at,
faggot?

07:40.059 --> 07:42.461
I'm sorry. I thought
you were in the doorway.

07:46.265 --> 07:47.966
I'll get back to you,
lieutenant.

07:47.968 --> 07:53.572
Um, let's just --
let's just go study.

07:55.842 --> 07:57.843
Tao:
I uploaded a photo of our bully,

07:57.845 --> 07:59.911
And now this new
facial-recognition software

07:59.913 --> 08:02.347
Will scan all the
security-camera
footage for a match.

08:02.349 --> 08:03.915
Lewis: <i>I don't know what</i>
<i>you're talking about, lady.</i>

08:03.917 --> 08:06.084
<i>I wasn't anywhere near</i>
<i>that ugly mall.</i>

08:06.086 --> 08:08.119
Were you at the park
last night?

08:08.121 --> 08:09.621
What park?

08:09.623 --> 08:12.290
The park between the mall
and michelle's house.

08:12.292 --> 08:14.359
Michelle? Oh.

08:14.361 --> 08:17.696
You mean mikey --
the tranny?

08:17.698 --> 08:19.364
