08:19.366 --> 08:22.200
I like to stay as far away
from that freak as I can.

08:22.202 --> 08:24.769
[ barking ]

08:29.609 --> 08:33.512
Really? Is that why you attacked
her last week in the bathroom,

08:33.514 --> 08:36.348
<i>Pulled her pants down,</i>
<i>took photographs?</i>

08:36.350 --> 08:38.216
<i>And posted them</i>
<i>all over the internet?</i>

08:38.218 --> 08:41.786
Look, it was using
the girls' toilet, man.

08:41.788 --> 08:43.989
Guys aren't allowed
in there.

08:43.991 --> 08:46.625
That's sick,
and everybody thinks so.

08:46.627 --> 08:48.193
I'm just the only person

08:48.195 --> 08:49.561
That had enough balls
to do something about it.

08:49.563 --> 08:51.196
You call michelle "it"?

08:51.198 --> 08:52.230
