it says it's not a guy,

08:56.036 --> 08:59.504
So it isn't anything,
and it needed a lesson.

08:59.506 --> 09:02.374
You call it a lesson?
We call it sexual battery.

09:02.376 --> 09:04.676
How old are you?
15. How old are you?

09:04.678 --> 09:07.045
