for a very long time.

09:09.516 --> 09:11.750
<i>It was a joke!</i>
<i>It wasn't funny!</i>

09:11.752 --> 09:13.318
This happened over a week ago,
man.

09:13.320 --> 09:15.086
Why are you guys
hassling me about it now?

09:15.088 --> 09:17.489
Because michelle
is missing.

09:17.491 --> 09:18.823
[ dog growling ]

09:18.825 --> 09:20.525
We got something!
Lieutenant, over here!

09:20.527 --> 09:21.760
Right here!

09:21.762 --> 09:23.495
[ barking ]
freak probably ran away.

09:23.497 --> 09:25.430
Look, I have ran off
plenty of times,

09:25.432 --> 09:28.333
<i>And you guys</i>
<i>have never come looking for me.</i>

09:28.335 --> 09:30.835
Do you think they'll treat you
like a boy or a girl in jail?

09:30.837 --> 09:32.103
I'm not going to jail.

09:32.105 --> 09:33.672
