to know why?

09:33.674 --> 09:39.477
Because mikey got
what <i>it</i> deserved.

09:41.013 --> 09:43.281
There lewis is --
7:09 p.M.

09:43.283 --> 09:45.350
Buzz: And look who's
right in front of him.

09:45.352 --> 09:49.454
Captain, we have lewis on camera
at the mall last night

09:49.456 --> 09:50.655
Within 15 feet
of michelle.

09:52.058 --> 09:56.861
Okay, lewis, you lied about
not being at the mall.

09:56.863 --> 09:58.797
You lied about
not seeing michelle.

09:58.799 --> 10:00.865
