drop kris off at her house

10:39.239 --> 10:41.006
And get you some dinner.

10:41.008 --> 10:42.574
But no burgers.

10:42.576 --> 10:44.709
Fine. Pizza, then.

10:46.145 --> 10:48.913
Oh, uh, did you guys find
that trans kid yet, or...?

10:50.449 --> 10:52.584
Her body.

10:54.320 --> 10:57.122
