11:17.010 --> 11:19.644
He wasn't, like,
a cross-dresser or anything.

11:19.646 --> 11:21.212
He just
liked other boys.

11:21.214 --> 11:24.182
Yeah,
I think that's how it works.

11:24.184 --> 11:27.385
Have you talked to
the victim's parents yet?

11:27.387 --> 11:31.823
No, but they're on their way in,
so...

11:31.825 --> 11:34.559
