11:35.962 --> 11:39.197
Come on, kids.
Let's go.

11:39.199 --> 11:41.332
Let's get
while the getting's good.

11:41.334 --> 11:44.202
I'll save you
a slice of something.

11:44.204 --> 11:46.037
