on the way home.

11:49.875 --> 11:52.210
Deanna, take a mold

11:52.212 --> 11:53.712
Of this impression
from the shovel, please?

11:53.714 --> 11:54.713
Uh-huh.

11:54.715 --> 11:56.347
[ police radio chatter ]

11:56.349 --> 11:58.083
Patrick,
take pictures of all of this.

11:58.085 --> 11:59.651
[ camera shutter clicking ]

11:59.653 --> 12:03.021
